headline: Is Celsius Still a Good Value After the 53% Rally and PepsiCo Distribution Milestone?
summary: Thinking about what to do with your Celsius Holdings shares, or considering a new position? You’re definitely not alone. The stock has been on a wild ride that’s hard to ignore. With a 53.3% gain over the past year, a 75.8% return over the last three years, and an 850.4% increase over five years, it’s clear that market enthusiasm for Celsius has rewarded early believers in a big way.
